msgid ""
"The projects: Projects are created from the file menu and then filled with "
"data to burn"
msgstr ""
"Projekti: Projekti se stvaraju iz padajućeg menija, a zatim ispune podacima "
"za upis."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
